      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey im working on my dissertation and im stuck on a bit of interpretation. if i have a p-value of 0.06 in my primary analysis, can i say there is a \"trend toward significance\" or is that actually scientifically valid? i want to make sure i'm not misrepresenting the null hypothesis.",
